{
  "stem": "10549.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When the war broke out-- at that time, my whole life changed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We fled our city where we used to live because we knew that it was a border town.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we fled.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went with my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother went with my sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we fled the, the city because we knew that in case-- when the war broke out, the city where we used to live was going to be right at the beginning of the front.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we just went deeper to the east, like 20 miles, 25 miles away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sosnowice.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "S-O-S-N-O-W-I-C-E.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Also Poland.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was Poland, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In that town, I stayed with my father for about three, four months.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew where they went, but that was the last time I saw my mother, when we separated, because she went to friends of ours in a-- further away to a different city.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I never seen my mother again after that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the circumstances was, it was much easier to travel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we wanted [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] go later on-- we had plans to meet my-- meet up with my mother and my sister, but that was impossible, because we couldn't travel.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a restriction of traveling right after that and for Jews especially.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could not leave the city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were restricted only to, to the city where we were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And right away, they made all kind of restriction.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we just stayed where we were, and we couldn't go out there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I found out later on that my sister went to Russia, because right after the war broke out with, between Germany and Russia, she went to Russia, where she lived through in Russia.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not exactly.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
